org.openrdf.query

Class QueryLanguage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openrdf.query.QueryLanguage

  • public class QueryLanguage
extends Object
    A type-safe enumeration for RDF query languages. QueryLanguage objects are identified by their name, which is treated in as case-insensitive way.
